p.k: Thinking it's a way to reconnect with her father Raven enters a beauty pageant. / The Titans must find a way to keep all the Jump City residents from moving to Stockton. / After the other Titans are turned into collectibles and disappear Robin must search yard sales and stores to find them. / Control Freak forces the Titans and the Scooby Gang to compete on Family Feud. / Robin tries to tell some Greek myths but the other Titans give their own fractured versions instead.
